 grew up around him, and he became the patron saint of Greece and of Russia, as well as of children, sailors, merchants, and pawnbrokers. His feast day is  6 December , and among the many roles which legend has assigned to him is that of bringer of Christmas presents, in the guise of ‘Santa Claus’ (an alteration of the Dutch form of his name, <i>Sinterklaas</i>)."]},{"name":"Nels","meanings":["vernacular form of   Niklas ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Nils fGregersson Stierna till Saby Haradshovding i Vastra Harad was born in 1400, in Säby, Jönköping, Sweden, his father, Greger Nilsson Stiera Stie, was 30 and his mother, Okan maka till Greger Nilsson, was 23. He had at least 6 sons and 2 daughters with Ingrid Jonsdotter Rosenbielke till Sandsjo. He died in 1431, in Bäckaby, Jönköping, Sweden, at the age of 31."},"et":{"1400–1431":"1400–1431","1405–1463":"1405–1463","1420–1495":"1420–1495","1425–1484":"1425–1484","1425–1695":"1425–1695","1427–1518":"1427–1518","1429–1463":"1429–1463","1430–1498":"1430–1498","–Female":"Surnud","1370–1400":"1370–1400","1377–Female":"1377–Surnud","1484":"1484","1495":"1495","1370":"1370","omkring 1425":"umbes 1425","1425":"1425","1400":"1400","1377":"1377","1498":"1498","1420":"1420","1431":"1431","1695":"1695","1430":"1430","1463":"1463","1518":"1518","1429":"1429","after 1400":"pärast 1400","1427":"1427","1405":"1405","Bäckaby, Jönköping, Sweden":"Bäckaby, Jönköping, Rootsi","Bäckaby, Jönköping, Sverige":"Bäckaby, Jönköping, Rootsi","Sweden":"Rootsi","Uppland, Sweden":"Uppland, Rootsi","Främsbacka, Stora Kopparberg, Dalarna":"Stora Kopparberg, Dalarna, Rootsi","Säby, Jönköping, Sweden":"Säby, Jönköping, Rootsi","Bäckaby":"Bäckaby, Jönköping, Rootsi"},"fi":{"1400–1431":"1400–1431","1405–1463":"1405–1463","1420–1495":"1420–1495","1425–1484":"1425–1484","1425–1695":"1425–1695","1427–1518":"1427–1518","1429–1463":"1429–1463","1430–1498":"1430–1498","–Female":"Kuollut","1370–1400":"1370–1400","1377–Female":"1377–Kuollut","1484":"1484","1495":